<text id="WB_KL-71">
	<metadata>
		<title>"Bear Hunting"</title>
			<author> Nettie <alph>Reuben</alph></author>
			<date>1957</date>
			<publication>William Bright, <em>The Karok Language</em> (1957), pp. 284-285, Text 71</publication>
	</metadata>
	<data>
		<paragraph>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w gl="the bear"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="6574">vírusar</m></w>
					<w><m id="3178">íshyaav</m></w>
					<w gl="December"><m id="4094">kusrah</m><m id="3790">kêem</m></w>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="3930">koovúra</m></w>
					<w gl="to animal den"><m id="1256">eeráriiv</m><m id="232">ak</m></w>
					<w><m id="4077">kúuk</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>
					<w gl="they go back to"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2674">pá</m><m id="3489">vyiihma</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>In the winter, in December (the bad month), the bears all go into dens.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w><m id="5502">sú'</m></w>
					<w gl="they live"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="1974">íkrii</m></w>
					<w gl="all winter"><m id="7097">ithé</m><m id="3178">eshyaav</m></w>.				
				</kar>
			<eng>They stay inside all winter.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
				  	<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>					
					<w gl="they say"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4823">píip</m></w>"
					<w><m id="1144">chími</m></w>					
					<w gl="our den"><m id="4327">nanu</m><m id="1256">'eeráriiv</m></w>
					<w gl="we look at them"><m id="4370">nu</m><m id="2674">p</m><m id="3489">imús</m><m id="269">an</m></w>."
				</kar>
			<eng>Then people used to say, "Let’s go look at our dens!"</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they look at them"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2674">p</m><m id="3489">imús</m><m id="269">an</m></w>.									
				</kar>
			<eng>So they went to look at them.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>					
					<w gl="they say"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4823">píip</m></w>"		
					<w><m id="1144">chími</m></w>					
					<w gl="come out"><m id="6618">vôonupuk</m><m id="1419">i</m></w>."
				</kar>
			<eng>And they said, "Come out!"</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
				<w gl="nowhere"><m id="5104">púra fát</m><m id="232">aak</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>(The bear) was nowhere to be seen.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
					<w><m id="5156">puxích</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they shout"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="1624">íhyiv</m></w>"
					<w><m id="1144">chími</m></w>					
					<w gl="come out"><m id="6618">vôonupuk</m><m id="1419">i</m></w>."
				</kar>
			<eng>So they shouted loudly, ‘Come out!’</eng>
			</s>			
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w gl="so"><m id="6570">víri</m><m id="6377">va</m></w>
					<w gl="nowhere"><m id="5104">púra fát</m><m id="232">aak</m></w>
					<w gl="he is not coming out"><m id="6618">vôonupuk</m><m id="6035">tih</m><m id="1371">ara</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>(The bear) He didn’t come out anywhere.</eng>
			</s>	
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w gl="he crawled in"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">u</m><m id="6609">vôonkaa</m></w>		
					<w gl="the man"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="833">'ávansa</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>So the man crawled in.</eng>
			</s>				
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="1649">îikam</m></w>
					<w><m id="7097">yítha</m></w>
					<w gl="he stays"><m id="6175">ú</m><m id="1974">krii</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>And one stayed outside.</eng>
			</s>	
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w gl="visible"><m id="7038">yanav</m><m id="1729">éek</m></w>
					<w gl="he lies curled"><m id="6175">u</m><m id="5626">tákviihriv</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>(The one who crawled in) saw (the bear) curled up.</eng>
			</s>	
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w gl="he has"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">óo</m></w>
					<w gl="push outside"><m id="3577">yfúutrupuk</m></w> 
					<w gl="the bear"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="6574">vírusar</m></w>,
					<w><m id="1657">îim</m></w> 
					<w gl="he came out"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">u</m><m id="6618">vôonupuk</m></w>.		
				</kar>
			<eng>Then he pushed the bear outside, he came out.</eng>
			</s>				
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w gl="he has"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">óo</m></w>
					<w gl="come back out"><m id="2674">p</m><m id="6618">vôonupuk</m></w>
					<w gl="the person"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="506">'áraar</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>The person came back outside.</eng>
			</s>			
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w gl="the one outdoors"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="1657">'îim</m></w> 
					<w gl="who stays"><m id="1974">ikrêe</m><m id="369">n</m></w> 
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w gl="he has"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">óo</m></w>
					<w><m id="3580">ykar</m></w>
					<w gl="the bear"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="6574">vírusar</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>And the one who stayed outside killed the bear.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they finished slaughtering it" ><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="5055">piykáravar</m></w>,
					<w gl="out of the den"><m id="1256">eeráriiv</m><m id="232">ak</m></w>
					<w gl="they drag it out"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="3374">ithyúrurupuk</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>They finished killing it, they dragged it out of the den.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w><m id="3178">íshyaav</m></w>
					<w gl="they are killing it that way"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4004">kupee</m><m id="3580">ykára</m><m id="1356">hi</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>They killed it that way in the winter.</eng>
			</s>			
 </paragraph>	
	<paragraph>			
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w gl="when"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they carry it in"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="3304">íthviish</m></w>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
					<w><m id="780">athkúrikar</m></w>
					<w gl="when PERF"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they skin it"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2959">íshfir</m></w>
					<w gl="its skin"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="4260">mú</m><m id="4148">maan</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>When they brought it in, (the bear) was fat when they skinned its hide.</eng>
			</s>			
			
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w><m id="1649">îikam</m></w>
					<w gl="big fire"><m id="10">áh</m><m id="3668">kaam</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they make it"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="2348">íkyav</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>So they made a big fire outdoors.</eng>
			</s>			
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="6381">vaa</m></w>
					<w><m id="16">áak</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they make it"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="4651">pathríimkurih</m></w>.				
				</kar>
			<eng>And they spread (the hide) over the fire.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="6570">víri</m></w>	
					<w gl="the fat"><m id="4407">pa</m><m id="779">athkúrit</m></w>
					<w gl="it has"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">óo</m></w>
					<w gl="it runs together"><m id="3282">thrîish</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>So the fat ran together.</eng>
			</s>			
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they pull it out"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="3372">ithyúruripaa</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>Then they dragged it out of the fire.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6675">vúra</m></w>
					<w><m id="4352">nîinamich</m></w>
					<w gl="it became"><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">u</m><m id="560">'árihish</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>Then it became small.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they scrape it"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="5779">taxíshxish</m></w>	
					<w gl="when it is"><m id="4408">pa</m><m id="5506">t</m><m id="6175">óo</m></w>		
					<w><m id="2498">msip</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>And they scraped it when it was cool.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3745">kári</m></w>
					<w><m id="6847">xás</m></w>
					<w><m id="6381">vaa</m></w>
					<w><m id="5506">tá</m></w>		
					<w gl="they cut it up"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="6659">vupákpak</m></w>.					
				</kar>
			<eng>And they cut it up.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="5163">púyava</m></w>
					<w><m id="6381">vaa</m></w>
					<w><m id="3178">íshyaav</m></w>
					<w gl="they were eating it"><m id="3977">kun</m><m id="814">'áam</m><m id="6035">tih</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>And in the winter they ate it.</eng>
			</s>
			<s>
				<kar>
					<w><m id="3839">kimkuv</m></w>.
				</kar>
			<eng>It was (called) kimkuv. </eng>
			</s>													
		</paragraph>
	</data>
